snippet.textDisplay:
From experiment part its a good effort by adit and the team. There are few places I lost my interest, transitions were somehow lost in between yet kept me eager to explore more. To me Arnob's part was the soothing one and last trnasition just blown me way. Sunidhi as a (usually) Rabindra sangeet Singer had been outstanding from classical part of the arrangement. The song seemed a bit clumsy but the beat was interesting. Guitar and classical strings complemented the song very well. About brass section, it was interesting but some places it was causing a bit discomfort in my ears. 

This song is a good one but you know being part of the musical journey as fan, I expected something  more blasting in arnob's way. May be I am habituated with arnob that way. I actually expected something more like chiltey rod, calm and soothing but with arnob's kinda vibrance. 

In the end, I do really appreciate the effort. May not be my most favourite from CSB but well recieved for the experiment part of view. 

Yeah, may be a little bit dissappointed !!! What can I do really, they settled the expectation bar so high so Not the  best one but better than many other prevoiusly released songs.

snippet.textDisplay: The male part is written by Divash Krishna Biswas? That is very well written, out of this world to be honest just like this composition, takes one to a different dimension. The synth bass sounds mezmerizing, can't wait to hear it with a proper subwoofer. Now, I'm not knowledgeable enough to understand all the intricacies of song composition and context behind Raag Emon, but the 5:50 transition throws me off a bit. Listening it on repeat makes my ears ignore it now. It's almost like climbing stairs and all on a sudden there's a bigger step if that makes any sense. Maybe a milliscond too soon. So many great songs coming out of this effort it's becoming impossible to pick favorites. Wil Coke Studio make some vinyl records of the seasons please?

What a beautiful blend of modern & classical! The true range of Bangla music. Amazingly delivered by the lead couple Arnob & Sunidhi. ‘Bela Haray’ part also demands to be a standalone song. 

Adit’s music arrangement was outstanding. 

The ending was so soothing when Arnob & Sunidhi looked at each other. ❤

snippet.textDisplay: কোক স্টুডিও বাংলার আয়জোন গুলো সব অসাধারন  যেমন গান, নাটক,মিউশিয়ান,লাইটিং সাউন্ড সব কিছু । তবুও একপেশে কিছু না করে যারা বাংলা সংগীত কে অনেক ঋনি করেছেন এখনও করে যাচ্ছেন তাদের কে সম্মানিত করলে নতুন কিছুর মাধ্যমে !তাহলে কোক স্টুডিও বাংলার সম্মান আরো বাড়বে । কোক স্টুডিও দেশে দেশে বেলা হারানোর আগে কোক স্টুডিও বাংলা সারা দুনিয়ার বিস্ময় হয়ে থাক শুভ কামনা ।।❤❤❤❤
